OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fpossible, especially across the
OL,8,FPennines where some heavier bursts may
OL,9,Foccur and hill fog will develop. Gusty
OL,10,Fwinds also strengthen overnight and
OL,11,Fpersist into tomorrow morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloudy with hill fog across
OL,14,Fthe Pennines, and light rain gradually
OL,15,Feasing but giving way to showers.
OL,16,FElsewhere, mostly cloudy to start but
OL,17,Fsome bright spells develop later.
OL,18,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
